<paragraph id="BC429EA50A14DAA8C80B7415AEA0840C" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1A97B119636F58F60464DDAD53D3592B" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">An uncommon Bolivian endemic growing in scattered populations below 500 m in scrub and on forest margins around the northern and western fringes of the Chaco.</paragraph>
