<subSubSection id="BA6BBE251134C15B2EC337957DC1C272" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="notes">
<paragraph id="348539747BF7F7BCFBED85A498615835" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Note.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A6EABFB16F45030E59328422DCCD99B5" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">A very distinctive species because of its persistent foliose bracteoles combined with the coriaceous, convex sepals.</paragraph>
